# 193.16.20.35/29
## **NETWORK IP**
11000001 . 00010000 . 00010100 . 00100011 - IP  
11111111 . 11111111 . 11111111 . 11111000  - MASK

Newtwork Ip = Mask && ip 

**11000001 . 00010000 . 00010100 . 00100 000**
**193.16.20.32**

## **No of Host**

remaining mask ^ 2 - 2
32 - 29 = 3  
3 ^ 2 = 8  
8 - 2 = 6

no of host is **6**
